I think I was the first kid to get hand-me-ups.

69
00:02:54,975 --> 00:02:56,320
太小了。
It's too small,

70
00:02:56,321 --> 00:02:57,817
过时了。
it's out of style,

71
00:02:57,818 --> 00:02:59,495
又不酷。
and it's just not cool.

72
00:02:59,496 --> 00:03:00,955
穿衣服不是为了装酷，
It ain't supposed to be cool.

73
00:03:00,956 --> 00:03:02,455
而是为了保暖。
It's supposed to be warm.

74
00:03:02,456 --> 00:03:03,992
保暖就足够了。
Being warm is cool.

75
00:03:03,993 --> 00:03:05,531
我不是要你出钱。
I'm not asking you to buy it.

76
00:03:05,532 --> 00:03:06,840
