I'll save up.

77
00:03:06,841 --> 00:03:08,374
存什么钱？
Save up what?

78
00:03:08,375 --> 00:03:10,617
存你给我零花钱？
I was hoping you can give me an allowance.

79
00:03:12,350 --> 00:03:14,857
<i>我知道这个要求很白痴。</i>
I know it sounded like an innocent enough question,

80
00:03:14,858 --> 00:03:16,719
