but here's what he heard.

81
00:03:16,720 --> 00:03:18,086
你每天象奴隶一样工作，
Since you work like a slave all day

82
00:03:18,087 --> 00:03:19,813
却没有机会花钱，
and don't have any time to enjoy your own money,

83
00:03:19,814 --> 00:03:21,465
不如，我帮你花。
can I have it?

84
00:03:24,231 --> 00:03:26,871
我不会给你这个无所事事的臭小子一分钱。
I'm not giving you money for walking around doing nothing.

85
00:03:27,140 --> 00:03:28,769
零花钱？！
An allowance?

86
00:03:28,770 --> 00:03:30,898
我让你睡在我家里，
I'll allow you to sleep here at night.

87
00:03:30,899 --> 00:03:33,010
我允许你吃我的土豆
I'll allow you to eat them potatoes.

88
00:03:33,067 --> 00:03:35,150
我允许你用我的电灯。
I'll allow you to use my lights.

89
00:03:35,151 --> 00:03:37,266
我允许你喝我的汽水。
I'll allow you to drink my Kool-Aid.

90
00:03:37,267 --> 00:03:39,493
我允许你吃我的绿豆……
I'll allow you to nibble on them green beans.

91
00:03:39,494 --> 00:03:42,070
我允许你看我的电视
I'll allow you to look at that TV.

92
00:03:42,071 --> 00:03:44,178
我允许你用我的煤气
I'll allow you to run up my gas bill.

93
00:03:44,179 --> 00:03:46,368
我允许你在我家里晃悠
I'll allow you to walk up my stairs.

94
00:03:46,369 --> 00:03:49,822
我允许你向我提出这样荒谬的要求
I'll allow you to ask me these ridiculous-ass questions.

95
00:03:49,823 --> 00:03:51,593
你还指望我给你零用钱？
Why should I give you an allowance

96
00:03:51,594 --> 00:03:54,529
你做的一起都是我在买单。
when I already paid for everything you do?

97
00:03:54,684 --> 00:03:57,270
你见过谁有零用钱？
Who you know that gets an allowance?

98
00:03:56,578 --> 00:03:57,578
Huh?

99
00:03:58,191 --> 00:03:59,827
训话完毕！
I'm finished.

100
00:04:00,213 --> 00:04:03,874
格根就有零用钱。 他老爸每周给他5元。
I was talking to Greg and

101
00:04:01,915 --> 00:04:03,987
he said that he gets five dollars a week.

102
00:04:03,875 --> 00:04:06,197
听起来，他老爸比我厚道，
Sounds like Greg's doing better than me.

103
00:04:06,198 --> 00:04:08,099
你就找他老爸要钱去吧，
Ask him for an allowance.

104
00:04:08,100 --> 00:04:09,677
你想买皮甲克，
You want to buy a leather coat,

105
00:04:09,942 --> 00:04:13,003
你必须自己挣钱。
you  need to get a leather-coat job.

106
00:04:13,350 --> 00:04:15,570
<i>老爸不在家的时候，</i>
While things might have been tight with my father,

107
00:04:15,571 --> 00:04:17,484
<i>老妈很休闲。</i>
my mother was getting loose.

108
00:04:17,485 --> 00:04:20,476
<i>独自在家的时候，她总是很开心，</i>
She was always happy when she had the house to herself.

109
00:04:21,515 --> 00:04:23,769
<i>看看小报</i>
She caught up on her reading.

110
00:04:23,770 --> 00:04:26,798
<i>煲煲电话</i>
She talked on the phone.

111
00:04:26,799 --> 00:04:29,567
<i>偷吃很贵的零食，还是背着我们藏起来的。</i>
She  ate expensive candy she hid from us.

112
00:04:29,913 --> 00:04:34,438
<i>但总有一些意想不到的事情打断她……</i>
But there was one thing that she never counted on to mess up her day.

113
00:04:36,900 --> 00:04:38,057
请进
Coming...

114
