味道好极了
Mmm.

120
00:04:57,620 --> 00:04:58,620
This is good!

121
00:05:00,646 --> 00:05:04,099
<i>如果不是嘴馋，我们不会吃这些“特种材料”。</i>
If we had ladders, he'd have ate the asbestos.

122
00:05:03,522 --> 00:05:05,177
I want one! Me, too! Me, too!

123
00:05:05,827 --> 00:05:07,560
给我留一点?
Me, too! Come on, me too!

124
00:05:09,042 --> 00:05:12,566
