cause I'm cleaning up.

127
00:05:15,349 --> 00:05:16,858
What are we going to do all day?

128
00:05:17,274 --> 00:05:18,158
随便
I don't know.

129
00:05:18,159 --> 00:05:19,919
自己玩吧
Go play.

130
00:05:20,572 --> 00:05:24,271
在4:30之前，别弄乱了房子。
