they play one of the cheapest games ever invented:

139
00:05:43,163 --> 00:05:44,661
“赌你不敢！"
"I Dare You."

140
00:05:44,662 --> 00:05:49,176
我赌你不敢把这些冰放到衣服里。
I dare you to put these ice cubes under your armpit.

141
00:05:49,713 --> 00:05:52,352
