Whoo!

145
00:05:56,587 --> 00:05:57,644
One...

146
00:05:58,677 --> 00:05:59,698
two...

147
00:06:00,237 --> 00:06:01,620
数得太慢了，塔尼亚。
Count it normal, Tonya...

148
00:06:01,621 --> 00:06:04,092
