three...

149
00:06:04,093 --> 00:06:07,120
我赌他不敢把冰放到衣服里。
Girl, what is wrong with you?

150
00:06:04,480 --> 00:06:06,924
I dared him to put ice cubes under his arms.

151
00:06:07,121 --> 00:06:09,389
