Not... in the glass.

153
00:06:12,934 --> 00:06:15,296
我们还要喝水呢。
Boy, people got to drink from that.

154
00:06:15,297 --> 00:06:17,349
呵呵，我赌你不敢喝。
Okay, I dare you to drink it.

155
00:06:17,349 --> 00:06:19,229
千万别喝? 很脏。
You better not. That's nasty.

156
00:06:19,229 --> 00:06:20,189
