163
00:06:31,934 --> 00:06:33,508
相 当 无聊！
Two walls.

164
00:06:33,509 --> 00:06:35,461
你必须喝了。
Now you have to do something.

165
00:06:35,462 --> 00:06:36,576
太脏了。
That's nasty.

166
00:06:36,577 --> 00:06:39,792
